<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - Movie Database</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #2c3e50;
            background: #34495e;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, #3498db 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 75% 75%, #9b59b6 0%, transparent 50%);
            background-size: 100px 100px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: rgba(236, 240, 241, 0.9);
            padding: 1.2rem 0;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 3px solid #ecf0f1;
        }
        
        .nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        
        .nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.3rem;
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            text-transform: lowercase;
        }
        
        .nav a:hover {
            background: #c0392b;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            border: 2px solid #95a5a6;
        }
        
        .content {
            background: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border-left: 6px solid #f39c12;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            text-decoration: underline;
            text-decoration-color: #f39c12;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #34495e;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        
        th, td {
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        
        th {
            background: #95a5a6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        tr:hover {
            background-color: #bdc3c7;
            transform: scale(1.01);
            transition: all 0.15s ease;
        }
        
        .error {
            background: #ff6b6b;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        
        .welcome-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .welcome-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a3f8a, #2d1b69);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .welcome-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .welcome-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            color: #95a5a6;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #f39c12;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .personal-note {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <nav class="nav">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/actors">Actors</a>
                <a href="/directors">Directors</a>
                <a href="/genres">Genres</a>
                <a href="/movies">Movies</a>
                <a href="/productions">Productions</a>
                <a href="/streaming-platforms">Streaming Platforms</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="personal-note">
                <strong>Hey there!</strong> Welcome to my movie database project. I built this during my coding bootcamp to practice backend development. Still learning, but pretty proud of how it turned out! - Susan üé¨
            </div>
            <%- body %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            Built with ‚ù§Ô∏è by Susan | Mississippi Coding Academies Student | 
            <a href="https://github.com/7windhams/MOVIE-APP-PROJECT">View on GitHub</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>